name: Silence in a deepest night
description: Life during the day often makes us forget the spiritual things that are so important. Maybe we are always carried away to physical material or even to the world of the digital universe which is all created by humans. I need time to reflect again before the morning asks me to scream to wake up the sleeping people. I have to be quiet and calm to rearrange the positive ions in my soul. Then I meditate in the middle of the night till the morning call me.
